        public static java.util.List<com.squareup.okhttp.internal.spdy.Header> createRequestHeaders(io.grpc.Metadata.Headers headers,

        Serializes the given headers and creates a list of OkHttp Headers to be used when creating a stream. Since this serializes the headers, this method should be called in the application thread context.
